{"tid":2366212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★call g群組？「廟街疫區」患者增至27宗","createTime":"2021-01-14T10:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T12:48:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3f807eee00daacbf01122b9f1cdb1aea9c454ddd","tid":2366212,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情持續，最新油尖旺成為疫區。截至昨日（13日）的兩周內，油尖旺區累計81宗個案，當中「廟街疫區」佔27宗，患者居於新填地街20至26號 （雙數）門牌唐樓，其他則居廣東道、廟街等。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君今日（14日）表示，區內最初爆發來自中九龍幹線及將軍澳藍田隧道工人群組，大部分人士是尼泊爾裔，他們很多家庭成員，可能會有家庭或親友傳播；今日新填地街24號再多一宗確診及一宗初步確診個案，24號門牌唐樓首次失守，20至26號樓宇共用出入口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/574505/新冠肺炎-廟街疫區-患者增至27宗-新填地街24號首現患者\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F574505%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BB%9F%E8%A1%97%E7%96%AB%E5%8D%80-%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B327%E5%AE%97-%E6%96%B0%E5%A1%AB%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%9724%E8%99%9F%E9%A6%96%E7%8F%BE%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=ab43d6e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/574505/新冠肺炎-廟街疫區-患者增至27宗-新填地街24號首現患者</a>"},{"pid":"6c5a402c93b07d2737554d712eab3bcc9d5859e3","tid":2366212,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122e48142e8b743cc59502c07755535f5133703a","tid":2366212,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:12:44.000Z","msg":"@蓋"},{"pid":"c774cd2b1d10832c83b82d166f3659ca1fd806e8","tid":2366212,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"122e48142e8b743cc59502c07755535